results.title: Live Laugh Love- Modern Art Print
results.description:
Welcome to my shop Rock Maple Sugar! I create prints for the home, for weddings, family, children, many of them personalised. The prints are sold WITHOUT FRAME.

LIVE LAUGH LOVE

SIZE
I can provide these prints in: 
A4 (210mm x 297mm) 
A3 (297cm x 420cm).  ONLY TO GERMANY

QUALITY
My prints are printed out on very high Quality Epson Archival Matte Paper, 192g/m2. I use a photo lab quality Canon colour printer , the PIXMA PRO 100S, set at the highest quality setting using the original Canon ink cartridges. The colours are crisp, clean and vibrant. Please note that the colours on your monitor may vary slightly from the printed art.

SHIPPING
I will ship within 3 to 5 days of the order placement using Deutsche Post. Within Germany the prints will arrive in 2-3 days, and internationally you can expect in 7-10 days, but sometimes 1-4 weeks depending on the country.
A4 and Letter size prints will be placed in a plastic sleeve and then in a reinforced envelope to ensure safe delivery. 
A3 prints are put it a plastic sleeve and send in a strong cardboard tube. Both are labelled with a big red DO NOT BEND sticker.
The prices for theA3  prints are based on the different shipping charges required for A3 prints. As I cannot change the shipping charges for these prints, I have included the shipping charges in the price of the print.
Shipping charges includes the cost of the packaging materials and the postage, nothing more. It is unfortunately very expensive to ship the tubes from Germany, so I would recommend purchasing the digital file instead and get it printed yourself.

PLEASE NOTE THE PRINTS ARE SOLD WITHOUT FRAME. I recommend the IKEA RIBBA frame 30cm x 40cm for €5,99.

QUESTIONS?
If you have any questions at all, don't hesitate to contact me.
I am a friendly and service-oriented seller and look forward to hearing from you!
